title: Prank Calling Waffle House
description:
Need a pick me up? This week on Unfazed and Unbothered Tasia and Camo bring in the laughs calling local fast food spots and pranking them. From chicken nuggets with a bird beak in them and employees calling Tasia a B**** with bad hair, there is no bars held with these two. "Can I speak to the manager?" reaches a whole new level this week. Tune in to hear it all unfold!
